        "cancellation": "In the event that you need to cancel your trip, the following charges will apply based on the total billing amount:\n\nInitial Cancellation: 30% of the total bill is non-refundable once the booking is confirmed.\n\n30 – 15 Days before Check-in: 50% of the total bill will be charged as a cancellation fee.\n\n15 – 07 Days before Check-in: 75% of the total bill will be charged as a cancellation fee.\n\nWithin 07 Days of Check-in: 100% of the total bill (No Refund).",
        "refund": "Refunds (if applicable after cancellation charges) are processed back to the original payment method.\n\nAccording to Yatravi's standard policy, refunds are typically processed within 5-7 business days.",
        "payment": "To ensure a seamless booking experience for your Songkran trip, we follow a structured payment schedule:\n\nBooking Token: 30% of the total package cost is required to initiate the booking.\n\nVoucher Issuance: 20% payment is due upon receipt of your booking vouchers.\n\nFinal Balance: The remaining 50% must be cleared 1 week before the trip departure.\n\nFull Payment: Total payment must be completed by the time of Check-in.\n\nDocumentation: A scanned copy of a valid ID proof is required for hotel reservations.\n\nModes of Payment:\n\nOnline: NEFT, IMPS, Google Pay, PhonePe, or UPI.\n\nIn-Person: Visit our office for direct payments.\n\nConvenience: Cash and Cheque pickup services are available within Office Only."
